post.author: 강동욱
post.content:
이사회 골프 일정이 아래와 같이 잡혔습니다.

1. 시간 : May 11 (Sat)
2. 장소 : Circle course at Station Creek (Formerly called, 'Gormley' ),
  * Direction : 404 North, get off at 'Stouffville(spelling ???) East,
                   at Woodbine, make a Left Turn to North .
                From Stouffville and Woodbine, 2 KM north on Right Hand Side.

3. How (Much) : $45 (Guest Fee)
4. Tee Off time : 12:48, 12:57, 1:05, 1:14, 1:22 (5 tee off times)
5. Come early and pick your own play mates.
* 코스카님에 의해서 게시물 이동되었습니다 (2003-05-24 01:38)
post.title: [행사안내] 이사회 골프일정
